actions.message:
------------------------------------------------
**Basic**
------------------------------------------------
Help                        - This Message
---
Suggestion                  - Sends a suggestion to my owner for new commands and such

------------------------------------------------
**Moderation**
------------------------------------------------
Purge (#ofmsgs)             - Deletes the specified amount of messages
---
Ban (user)                  - Bans someone
---
Kick (user)                 - Kicks Someone
---
Warnings (member)           - Show the current warning points for that member
---
Warn (member) (reason)      - Give the mentioned member 1 warning point. (if they reach 3, they will be banned)
---
SetWarns (member) (amount)  - Edit the mentioned users warning points
---
WarnLog (Channel)           - Set a log channel for the warnings

------------------------------------------------
**Miscellaneous**
------------------------------------------------
STimer (seconds)            - Sets a timer for the specified seconds
---
MTimer (minutes)            - Sets a timer for the specified minutes
---
BotInfo                     - Sends some info about the bot

------------------------------------------------
**Role Setting**
------------------------------------------------
RoleMenu                    - Walks you through setting up emoji roles
---
SetupTCH (channel)          - Sets the mentioned channel as the place to set the emoji roles.
---
(more to come)
